  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Construction Ships are mobile construction yards.<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>These very large ships spend most of their time buildin=
g mining
  stations at uninhabited, resource-rich planets and moons. However they can
  also build other specialized star bases anywhere in deep space.<o:p></o:p=
></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Construction ships are extremely valuable &#8211; they
  should always be escorted to protect against attacks from pirates or enemy
  empires. These ships are also expensive to maintain &#8211; only build th=
em
  as needed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Use the Cycle Construction Ships button to cycle through
  all the construction ships in your empire, or use the 'Y' key.<o:p></o:p>=
